| Type of Radiation   | Form                                           | Examples                                                    | Medium Needed                    |
| ------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| `Electromagnetic` | Waves (oscillating electric &amp; magnetic fields) | Radio, Microwave, Infrared, Visible Light, UV, X-ray, Gamma | No (travels in space)            |
| `Nuclear`         | Particles &amp; Waves from unstable nuclei         | Alpha (α), Beta (β), Gamma (γ)                              | No (comes from atoms)            |
| `Mechanical`      | Vibrations in matter                           | Sound, Seismic waves, Water waves                           | Yes (needs air, water, or solid) |



